1
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,400
Crown Prince.

2
00:01:42,239 --> 00:01:43,840
What brings you here today

3
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:45,640
to seek me out at the Music Bureau?

4
00:01:46,519 --> 00:01:47,280
We said

5
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:48,760
upon your triumphant return,

6
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:50,599
We would welcome you with a feast.

7
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,239
We had Yudie

8
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,239
prepare a table of wine and dishes.

9
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:03,319
Crown Prince,

10
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,200
whatever you wish to say,

11
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,840
please speak plainly.

12
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:10,840
To be honest,

13
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:12,319
We quite admire you.

14
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:13,520
You have talent,

15
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:14,479
strategy,

16
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,680
and courage.

17
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,439
However, now,

18
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,199
though you returned victorious,

19
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,479
by toppling the Left Chancellor,

20
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:23,840
you implicated most of the court.

21
00:02:24,159 --> 00:02:25,719
How many people's interests you've upset?

22
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:28,560
You've broken the rules.

23
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:32,159
Do you know how many people,

24
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,759
openly and secretly, want you dead?

25
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:37,639
Rules?

26
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:41,280
Are these rules to use any means necessary,

27
00:02:42,199 --> 00:02:43,039
to treat lives as worthless,

28
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:44,439
and bring suffering to all?

29
00:02:46,719 --> 00:02:47,439
If no one

30
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,159
is willing to break such rules,

31
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,840
then I shall be the first to do so.

32
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,479
Ning Chen,

33
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:58,319
your life is your own.

34
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,719
You must first stay alive

35
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:03,360
to have any chance to fulfill your ambitions.

36
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:05,680
Ideals are noble,

37
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:07,560
but reality is harsh.

38
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,520
We are the Crown Prince,

39
00:03:09,919 --> 00:03:11,319
the future Xuandi.

40
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,719
We can protect you,

41
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:14,039
protect Yudie,

42
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,719
protect everyone you care about.

43
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,280
Only then can you

44
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:19,840
better pursue your ambitions and ideals.

45
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:26,479
Your Highness,

46
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:29,280
is this a threat?

47
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,479
Ning Chen,

48
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:35,240
swift steeds are plentiful,

49
00:03:35,439 --> 00:03:36,840
but those who recognize them are rare.

50
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:39,400
We feel a kindred spirit in you,

51
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:41,039
and treasure your talent greatly.

52
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,199
As the heir to the throne,

53
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,479
We too wish to see

54
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:46,479
a realm of just and clear law,

55
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,199
peace and order across the land.

56
00:03:50,159 --> 00:03:51,360
What does Your Highness want of me?

57
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:52,840
Now We are

58
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:55,759
caught in the struggle for the throne.

59
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,360
Our position as Crown Prince teeters.

60
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:01,280
We want you

61
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:03,159
to be Our trusted advisor.

62
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:04,560
With our strengths combined,

63
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,319
you'll help Us steady the court

64
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,840
and gain a firm footing in the army.

65
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,280
Let Father see

66
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,800
that We are the only one

67
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:12,520
fit to inherit the throne.

68
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:17,199
If Your Highness devotes yourself to the people,

69
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,000
His Majesty will see it sooner or later.

70
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,879
And Your Highness

71
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:24,839
will eventually attain what you desire.

72
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,519
Ning Chen,

73
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:31,199
do you know how many covet Our position

74
00:04:31,319 --> 00:04:32,519
and want Us dead?

75
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:35,120
This is a dog-eat-dog world.

76
00:04:35,959 --> 00:04:37,279
Only by becoming strong yourself

77
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:39,079
can you do what you wish.

78
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:40,920
The day We ascend the throne,

79
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,480
you'll stand below only one,

80
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,519
and above all others.

81
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,519
What rule could not be broken?

82
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,160
What woman could not be had?

83
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:48,839
The path,

84
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:51,560
you chose it yourself.

85
00:04:52,399 --> 00:04:52,959
Your fate,

86
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,720
you chose it as well.

87
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:58,720
Her fate,

88
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:01,600
that too lies in your choice.

89
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,160
How to weigh it

90
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,839
rests entirely on a single thought of yours.

91
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,839
Your Highness's kindness,

92
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,519
I appreciate the thought.

93
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,360
Those of different paths

94
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:21,360
cannot plan together.

95
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,639
The hour grows late.

96
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:25,920
Crown Prince,

97
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,040
forgive me for not seeing you off.

98
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:44,399
Ning.

99
00:05:45,199 --> 00:05:46,639
I'm the one who dragged you into this.

100
00:05:48,759 --> 00:05:49,800
Don't talk nonsense.

101
00:05:51,759 --> 00:05:53,319
Threats and bribes? Such old tricks.

102
00:05:54,519 --> 00:05:55,399
You think I'd be afraid?

103
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:03,399
It's all right.

104
00:06:07,279 --> 00:06:07,800
It's all right.

105
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:45,439
So, you've come after all.

106
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,959
A hundred years of life,

107
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:58,000
nothing more than

108
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:07,120
a fleeting moment.

109
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,680
Clouds shift and change,

110
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:17,199
the world is ever uncertain.

111
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,639
Your Majesty, you toil day and night.

112
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,600
Have a drink and rest a while.

113
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:46,680
Very well.

114
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,279
Still the same taste as before.

115
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,199
Terrible news!

116
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:20,399
The Left Chancellor is dead!

117
00:08:23,319 --> 00:08:23,839
Who's there?

118
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:24,839
Seize him!

119
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:35,120
The... the Crown Prince!

120
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:54,399
Chen.

121
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:55,000
How is it?

122
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:57,399
He was poisoned to death.

123
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,639
The guards were off duty at the time.

124
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:01,639
Chen Lezhang arrived a step too late.

125
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,600
Our men are investigating now.

126
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:05,480
What about the Crown Prince?

127
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,600
He's been captured.

128
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:08,679
Once the investigation is complete,

129
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,759
I'll go to the palace to report at once.

130
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:19,840
Ning... Ning Chen!

131
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,440
You framed Us!

132
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,360
What do you mean?

133
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,399
You killed the Left Chancellor,

134
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:34,240
and then framed Us for it.

135
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:40,039
What a clever way to reap the rewards!

136
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,519
You think

137
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,399
just because Father favors you,

138
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:45,120
you can do whatever you please?

139
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:48,039
You want to use Huai'an to rise to power!

140
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,879
Let Us tell you,

141
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,000
that's nothing but wishful thinking!

142
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:53,480
Are you out of your mind?

143
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,759
I was at the Music Bureau all night.

144
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,240
I didn't even step out of the room.

145
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:58,399
You're the one who's crazy.

146
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:01,960
Only you knew Our whereabouts.

147
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:02,960
If not you, then who?

148
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,360
The moment We left the Music Bureau,

149
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,440
We received a secret letter,

150
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,480
telling Us to come to the Inspectorate

151
00:10:09,559 --> 00:10:11,399
to discuss a deal with the Left Chancellor.

152
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:13,720
Little did We know,

153
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,279
We fell into your trap.

154
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:19,120
I really overestimated you before.

155
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,039
With such a brilliant father,

156
00:10:22,559 --> 00:10:24,320
how did he end up with such a foolish son?

157
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,039
You...

158
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:25,879
Don't "you" me.

159
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:28,200
You were so eager to silence the Chancellor,

160
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:29,360
afraid he'd confess

161
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:31,039
that you're the mastermind of the gold mine case.

162
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,600
Yesterday, you tried to win me over at the Bureau

163
00:10:33,759 --> 00:10:34,720
for this very reason, didn't you?

164
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:37,759
Don't think I don't know.

165
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,360
You planted a mole in the Inspectorate.

166
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:43,000
You could sneak in and kill the Chancellor,

167
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,080
but you couldn't escape unscathed.

168
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:47,240
Utterly foolish.

169
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,360
That's all nonsense!

170
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,200
You...

171
00:10:51,799 --> 00:10:52,279
Guards!

172
00:10:52,919 --> 00:10:53,519
Guards!

173
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,919
We demand to see Father!

174
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,600
Guards!

175
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,440
We demand to see Father!

176
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,679
Guards!

177
00:10:59,879 --> 00:11:01,000
We demand to see Father!

178
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:03,519
I'm innocent!

179
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:09,039
What audacity!

180
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:10,039
Your Majesty,

181
00:11:10,799 --> 00:11:12,519
while investigating the gold mine case,

182
00:11:13,039 --> 00:11:14,399
your servant found this Inspectorate badge.

183
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,879
Your servant lacked time to report it.

184
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:19,600
Your servant is still investigating the mole.

185
00:11:20,159 --> 00:11:21,440
Outrageous!

186
00:11:22,039 --> 00:11:24,679
Even the mighty Inspectorate has been infiltrated.

187
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:27,720
All evidence now points to the Crown Prince.

188
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:28,799
Your servant believes

189
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,240
this matter runs very deep.

190
00:11:30,519 --> 00:11:31,840
The Left Chancellor alone

191
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,759
could not have stirred up such a storm.

192
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:34,960
Behind the Left Chancellor,

193
00:11:36,159 --> 00:11:37,840
there must be someone of immense power.

194
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,039
Who?

195
00:11:40,519 --> 00:11:41,120
If we suppose

196
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:43,200
the Crown Prince is the mastermind,

197
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:45,559
then his goal was to expand his power

198
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,679
and secure his position as heir.

199
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:47,799
Once the Chancellor was exposed,

200
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,960
he used the mole to silence him.

201
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,159
Failing to win your servant over,

202
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,639
he then framed your humble servant.

203
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:53,879
Such a theory

204
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,240
is not impossible.

205
00:12:09,279 --> 00:12:09,840
Mother.

206
00:12:10,279 --> 00:12:11,639
How could my brother do such a thing?

207
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,720
What should we do, Mother?

208
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,960
Huai'an.

209
00:12:15,559 --> 00:12:16,600
Don't panic just yet.

210
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,720
Given the Crown Prince's character,

211
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,320
he would never do such a thing.

212
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:21,639
There must be

213
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:23,159
some kind of misunderstanding.

214
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,600
We'll go in shortly...

215
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,399
Issue a decree.

216
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:27,240
The Crown Prince murdered the Left Chancellor

217
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,399
and plotted treason.

218
00:12:28,639 --> 00:12:29,960
He shall be executed in three days.

219
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:31,919
Mother!

220
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:35,440
Your Majesty!

221
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,840
His Majesty is coughing up blood!

222
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:41,480
He is coughing up blood! Your Majesty!

223
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:44,000
Your Majesty!

224
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:45,200
Father!

225
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:46,600
Your Majesty!

226
00:13:00,399 --> 00:13:01,720
How is His Majesty's condition?

227
00:13:02,799 --> 00:13:03,519
To answer Your Majesty,

228
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:05,639
His qi and blood violently surged,

229
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:07,159
which disrupted his heart's pulse,

230
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,279
causing his heart to stop.

231
00:13:08,639 --> 00:13:09,639
His life hangs by a thread.

232
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:12,000
He could perish at any moment.

233
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:15,120
What did His Majesty consume today?

234
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:18,480
Everything was as usual, nothing unusual.

235
00:13:21,279 --> 00:13:21,720
But...

236
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,840
The Imperial Medical Bureau must do everything possible.

237
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,720
If anything happens to His Majesty,

238
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,080
do not blame me for being merciless.

239
00:13:27,919 --> 00:13:28,399
Your servant...

240
00:13:28,519 --> 00:13:30,759
Your servant shall do his utmost.

241
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:33,600
Your Majesty.

242
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:34,399
Father.

243
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,960
By the Mandate of Heaven,

244
00:13:43,159 --> 00:13:44,399
Xuandi hereby decrees:

245
00:13:44,799 --> 00:13:47,159
The Crown Prince has manipulated the court,

246
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,720
formed factions for personal gain,

247
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:49,840
committed countless evil deeds,

248
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,559
and brought suffering to the people.

249
00:13:51,799 --> 00:13:53,799
We are deeply grieved.

250
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:57,360
Yet royalty and commoners are equal under the law.

251
00:13:57,840 --> 00:14:01,679
The Crown Prince shall be executed in three days.

252
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:04,240
So decreed.

253
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:06,639
Eunuch Quan,

254
00:14:06,759 --> 00:14:07,879
please tell Father for me,

255
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:09,480
We did not do this.

256
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,080
We did not do this!

257
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,480
Eunuch Quan!

258
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:13,720
Your Highness,

259
00:14:14,799 --> 00:14:15,960
please accept the decree.

260
00:14:25,799 --> 00:14:27,080
If you knew it would come to this,

261
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:30,159
why did you do it?

262
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:38,799
Father,

263
00:14:41,799 --> 00:14:44,159
you truly do not trust your son.

